Needed plugins:
npm i
npm i nodemailer express nodemailer-mailgun-transport dotenv -S
npm i express mongoose cors body-parser morgan --save
npm i concurrently –-save
npm install axios –-save


Needed APIs:
You need to create a DB at mongoDB and use it at server.js
You need to use mailgun and use their API key and Domain in mail.js'

Files:
Create config.js at root directory 
Add the needed credidentials mentioned above in that folder
In mail.js use your mailgun mail in from

Run server:
Running with concurrently so you can run server by:
npm run dev
